#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Local skill discovery over qmd collections.

Layer 0 (primary): Metadata-aware scorer — reads SKILL.md frontmatter
         (name, description, triggers, tags) with field-weighted scoring.
         Splits multi-word queries into individual terms for broad coverage.
Layer 1 (optional): CM context — curated playbook matches.
Layer 2 (fallback): QMD semantic search — only when metadata returns <3 results.
"""

